      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8410169369649938629, guid: f63230ab1983b6948bd4ddf124878b15, type: 3}
      propertyPath: lines.Array.data[4].text
      value: You can use the arrow keys (or AD!) to move)
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8410169369649938629, guid: f63230ab1983b6948bd4ddf124878b15, type: 3}
      propertyPath: lines.Array.data[5].text
      value: Use either space or c to jump...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8410169369649938629, guid: f63230ab1983b6948bd4ddf124878b15, type: 3}
      propertyPath: lines.Array.data[6].text
      value: And hold your mouse to shake salt!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8410169369649938629, guid: f63230ab1983b6948bd4ddf124878b15, type: 3}
      propertyPath: lines.Array.data[7].text
